### Personal Finance API manual tests
### 個人財務管理システム API 手動テスト
### 个人财务管理系统 API 手动测试

### Usage / 使い方 / 使用方法
### 1. Start Spring Boot.
### 2. Run login requests and copy data.token.
### 3. Paste tokens into @userToken / @adminToken.
### 4. Run protected API tests.
### 5. Test user passwords have been migrated to BCrypt. Plain input password is 123456.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = paste_user_token_here
@adminToken = paste_admin_token_here
@categoryId = 1
@recordId = 1


### =========================
### Auth / 認証 / 认证
### =========================

### Login USER / 一般ユーザーログイン / 普通用户登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "クマ",
  "password": "123456"
}


### Login ADMIN / 管理者ログイン / 管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}


### BCrypt check: wrong password should return Result(false, "密码错误", null)
### BCrypt 確認：誤ったパスワードは業務エラーとして返る
### BCrypt 验证：错误密码应返回业务错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "クマ",
  "password": "111111"
}


### BusinessException check: unknown user should return Result(false, "用户不存在", null)
### BusinessException 確認：存在しないユーザー
### BusinessException 验证：不存在的用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "not_exists_user",
  "password": "123456"
}


### Access /me without token should fail in interceptor
### token なしで /me にアクセスすると失敗
### 不带 token 访问 /me 应失败
GET {{baseUrl}}/me


### Access /me with invalid token should fail in interceptor
### 無効 token で /me にアクセスすると失敗
### 使用错误 token 访问 /me 应失败
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: invalid-token


### Get current user / 現在ユーザー取得 / 查看当前用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Logout / ログアウト / 退出登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### =========================
### User / ユーザー / 用户
### =========================

### Register temporary user
### 一時ユーザー登録
### 注册临时用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manual_test_user",
  "password": "123456"
}


### Validation check: short password
### バリデーション確認：短すぎるパスワード
### 参数校验：密码太短
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bad_user",
  "password": "123"
}


### Admin get all users
### 管理者：全ユーザー取得
### 管理员查询全部用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: {{adminToken}}


### USER access admin API should fail
### 一般ユーザーで管理者 API にアクセスすると失敗
### 普通用户访问管理员接口应失败
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Admin reset temporary user password
### 管理者：パスワードリセット
### 管理员重置密码
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/manual_test_user/password
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPassword": "123456"
}


### Admin delete temporary user
### 管理者：ユーザー削除
### 管理员删除临时用户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/manual_test_user
Authorization: {{adminToken}}


### Change current user password
### 現在ユーザーのパスワード変更
### 修改当前用户密码
PUT {{baseUrl}}/me/password
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "123456"
}


### =========================
### Category / カテゴリ / 分类
### =========================

### Get my categories
### 自分のカテゴリ取得
### 查询自己的分类
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-categories
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Add expense category
### 支出カテゴリ追加
### 新增支出分类
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-categories
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "手動テスト支出",
  "type": "expense"
}


### Add category with invalid type should return BusinessException result
### 不正なカテゴリタイプは業務エラー
### 分类类型错误应返回业务错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-categories
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "invalid",
  "type": "abc"
}


### Delete category
### カテゴリ削除
### 删除分类
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transaction-categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### =========================
### Record / 収支記録 / 收支记录
### =========================

### Add expense record
### 支出記録追加
### 新增支出记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{categoryId}},
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1200.50,
  "remark": "manual test",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-30"
}


### Get records page
### 収支記録ページング取得
### 分页查询收支记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/page?page=1&size=10
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Search records
### 複合条件検索
### 条件筛选分页查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/search?type=expense&page=1&size=10
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Invalid page should return BusinessException result
### 不正な page は業務エラー
### page 错误应返回业务错误
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/page?page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Amount zero should return BusinessException result
### 金額 0 は業務エラー
### 金额为 0 应返回业务错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{categoryId}},
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 0,
  "remark": "amount zero",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-30"
}


### Update record
### 記録更新
### 修改记录
PUT {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/{{recordId}}
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{categoryId}},
  "type": "expense",
  "amount": 1500,
  "remark": "updated manual test",
  "recordDate": "2026-06-30"
}


### Delete record
### 記録削除
### 删除记录
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/transaction-records/{{recordId}}
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### =========================
### Stats / 統計 / 统计
### =========================

### Monthly stats
### 月次統計
### 月度统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-stats/month?year=2026&month=6
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Expense category stats
### 支出カテゴリ別集計
### 支出分类统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-stats/category/expense?year=2026&month=6
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Expense type total
### 支出タイプ合計
### 支出类型总额
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-stats/type-total?type=expense&year=2026&month=6
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### Invalid month should return BusinessException result
### 不正な月は業務エラー
### 月份错误应返回业务错误
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-stats/month?year=2026&month=13
Authorization: {{userToken}}


### =========================
### AI / AI アシスタント / AI 助手
### =========================

### AI chat
### AI 相談
### AI 对话
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/chat
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "生活費を節約するためのアドバイスをください"
}
